--- Contradictory normalized facts are visible to the checker; the artifact
--- validator must not certify nodeFactsConsistent for this node.
search [1] in WHIPPLESCRIPT-CONSTRUCT-GRAPH :
  noCapabilityRequirements(memoryNode)
  nodeRequiresCapability(memoryNode, memoryQuery)
  =>*
  inconsistentNodeFacts(memoryNode) .

--- A node cannot be accepted when the normalized artifact does not provide
--- node fact consistency evidence.
